com.inqwell.any.client

Class AnyDocView.DelegatingDocument

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.inqwell.any.client.AnyDocView.DelegatingDocument
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Document
    Enclosing class:
    AnyDocView

    protected class AnyDocView.DelegatingDocument
extends Object
implements Document
    Intercepts the method calls defined by javax.swing.text.Document so that specific functionality can be imposed. The insertString and remove methods are currently the only ones implemented and call the Inq expressions installed with setInsertExpr and setRemoveExpr
